<HL>
   Shearson Lehman Said to Be Discussing
   Bailout Proposal for First Capital Life
   ----
   By Susan Pulliam
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
01/28/92
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A4
</SO>
<CO>
   AXP FCH
</CO>
