<HL>
   First Capital, Units
   File a Joint Plan
   To Reorganize
   ----
   By Earl C. Gottschalk Jr.
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
02/12/92
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE C11
</SO>
