<HL>
   Western Pacific Life Insurance Is Seized
   By Regulators Due to Stability Concerns
   ----
   By Rhonda L. Rundle
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
08/26/91
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A4
