<HL>
   First Executive
   Files Petition
   For Chapter 11
   ---
   But Move Contains Surprise:
   Company to Reorganize
   Instead of Liquidate
   ----
   By Rhonda L. Rundle
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
05/15/91
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A4
</SO>
<CO>
   F.CLC F.CNM FEXC
</CO>
<MS>
FINANCIAL (FIN)
</MS>
<IN>
