<HL>
   French Investors Offer Plan
   To Acquire Executive Life
   ---
   Proposal, Totaling $3 Billion,
   Still Must Clear Hurdles;
   Claimants Face Losses
   ----
   By Frederick Rose
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
08/08/91
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A3
</SO>
